text: Kerstin Peters (born 27 July 1967) is a German rowing coxswain. She competed in the women's eight event at the 1988 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1967 births Category:Living people Category:German female rowers Category:Olympic rowers of West Germany Category:Rowers at the 1988 Summer Olympics Category:Rowers from Berlin Category:Coxswains (rowing)
